                </svg>
            </a>feathers-localstorage
        </h1>
        <p><a href="https://github.com/feathersjs-ecosystem/feathers-localstorage/">feathers-localstorage</a> is a
            database service adapter that extends <a
                    href="https://github.com/feathersjs-ecosystem/feathers-localstorage/blob/master/memory.md">feathers-memory</a> and
            stores data in <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage" rel="nofollow">localStorage</a>
            in the browser or <a href="https://facebook.github.io/react-native/docs/asyncstorage.html" rel="nofollow">AsyncStorage</a>
            in React Native.</p>
        <div class="highlight highlight-source-shell">
            <pre><code class="hljs">$ npm install --save feathers-localstorage</code></pre>
        </div>
        <blockquote>
            <p><strong>Important:</strong> <code>feathers-localstorage</code> implements the <a
                        href="https://docs.feathersjs.com/api/databases/common.html" rel="nofollow">Feathers Common
                    database adapter API</a> and <a href="https://docs.feathersjs.com/api/databases/querying.html"
                                                    rel="nofollow">querying syntax</a>.</p>
        </blockquote>
